    dc:description "Fig. 52. Trilacuna hazara, new species, female (PBI_OON 15665). A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Same, ventral view. C. Same, lateral view. D. Carapace, dorsal view. E. Same, ventral view. F. Same, lateral view. G. Same, anterior view. H. Epigastric area, ventral view. I. internal female genitalia, ventral view. AS = anterior sclerite; AP = apodeme; PR = posterior receptacle." ;
